msgstr "/* translator: This message is not what it seems to be. */"

#: nls.xml:516(para)
msgid ""
"If you want to communicate something to the translator, such as about how a "
"message is intended to line up with other output, precede the occurrence of "
"the string with a comment that starts with <literal>translator</literal>, e."
